<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-970] Make hadoop version overridable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-970</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now, one cannot change the version of Apache Hadoop on which Apache Mahout depend without editing the pom.xml.&lt;br/&gt;
This ticket is about making this possible.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This would help ensuring Apache Mahout work well with more recent versions of Apache Hadoop without disruption.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12541026">MAHOUT-970</key>
